description: The Skrullian Skymaster is a fictional comic book superhero appearing in books published by Marvel Comics, usually those featuring the Squadron Supreme, a superhero team of which Skymaster is a member. The character is the Squadron's counterpart of the Martian Manhunter, a member of DC Comics' superhero team, the Justice League of America.
name: Skrullian Skymaster
powers: Superhuman strength greater than a normal Skrull
